info: Dutch Bros Inc. operates and franchises drive-thru shops. The company offers Dutch Bros hot and cold espresso-based beverages, and cold brew coffee products, as well as Blue Rebel energy drinks, tea, lemonade, smoothies, and other beverages through company-operated shops and online channels. It operates approximately 470 drive-thru coffee locations in 11 states. The company was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Grants Pass, Oregon.
